"Oh my." was all Hoist could say, his eyes widdened at the stream of
heat that could have belonged to the Pit. He drastically leap out of the
way, rolling along the ground, as he just narrowly missed the fire.
"Slag, this isn't a very bright place to do that." he pleaded.
